    "MissionGiver": "Headhunters",
    "Title": "Setting a Trap",
    "TitleKey": "HeadHunters_ShipAmbush_Intro_title_001",
    "Description": "Got an opportunity for someone eager to show off their flying skills. Headhunters have been running afoul of this numbrain flying a<EM4>~mission(AmbushTarget)</EM4> and we\u2019re gonna put a stop to it once and for all.\n\nYou\u2019re gonna help us set a trap for them. See, there\u2019s an <EM4>emission cloud</EM4> near <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> that they fly by frequently. \n\nHead there, hide inside the cloud by powering down your ship, and attack the asshole as soon as you see \u2018em and other single-seaters dumb enough to fly with them. It\u2019ll be all you for that first hit, but we\u2019ll put some support ships nearby to help finish the job. \n\nAnd in honor of this being your first surprise attack for us, there's a bonus of <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4> for the main contractor at the end of the job. \n\nStows out.",
    "DescriptionKey": "HeadHunters_ShipAmbush_Intro_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "Got an opportunity for someone eager to show off their flying skills. Headhunters have been running afoul of this numbrain flying a<EM4>[AmbushTarget]</EM4> and we\u2019re gonna put a stop to it once and for all.\n\nYou\u2019re gonna help us set a trap for them. See, there\u2019s an <EM4>emission cloud</EM4> near <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> that they fly by frequently. \n\nHead there, hide inside the cloud by powering down your ship, and attack the asshole as soon as you see \u2018em and other single-seaters dumb enough to fly with them. It\u2019ll be all you for that first hit, but we\u2019ll put some support ships nearby to help finish the job. \n\nAnd in honor of this being your first surprise attack for us, there's a bonus of <EM4>[ScripAmount] Council Scrip</EM4> for the main contractor at the end of the job. \n\nStows out.",
